OL,3,CMother's fear for her future as
OL,4,Cresidency rules set to double
OL,6,FWATCH: The full video report by ITV
OL,7,FMeridian's Juliette Fletcher
OL,9,FAn NHS healthcare worker from Witney
OL,10,Fhas spoken of her "stress" and
OL,11,Funcertainty after the government
OL,12,Fproposed doubling the time migrants
OL,13,Fmust live in the UK before they can
OL,14,Fstay permanently.
OL,16,FPetra Moyo moved from Zimbabwe to
OL,17,FOxfordshire in 2022 with her three
OL,18,Fchildren, seeking a better life and an
OL,19,Fopportunity to work in the care sector.
