OL,3,CMother's fear for her future as
OL,4,Cresidency rules set to double
OL,6,F"It makes me feel very stressful," she
OL,7,Ftold ITV Meridian. "As a person, as a
OL,8,Fmother, you want to settle, you want
OL,9,Fto be grounded, you want to plan for
OL,10,Fthe future.
OL,12,F"But it's so hard now because I don't
OL,13,Fknow what the plans are for tomorrow."
OL,15,FPetra, who says she chose the UK
OL,16,Fbecause of the "beautiful opportunity"
OL,17,Fto work in care, insists she is
OL,18,Fplaying her part in British society.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
