OL,3,CMother's fear for her future as
OL,4,Cresidency rules set to double
OL,6,F"I pay the taxes, I follow the rules.
OL,7,FI'm not looking at benefits or
OL,8,Fanything else," she said. "I just want
OL,9,Fthe Home Office to stick to the
OL,10,Fpromise that they gave me when I was
OL,11,Flooking at relocating."
OL,13,FThe Lib Dem MP for Witney, Charlie
OL,14,FMaynard, has taken Petra's fight to
OL,15,FParliament, arguing that any changes
OL,16,Fshould not apply retrospectively to
OL,17,Fthose already living and working here.
OL,19,FHe told ITV Meridian: "This is
OL,20,Fobviously cruel. This moving of the
OL,21,Fgoalposts makes it miles crueller.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
