OL,3,CMother's fear for her future as
OL,4,Cresidency rules set to double
OL,6,F"I fundamentally feel, as the 300
OL,7,Fconstituents have written in about
OL,8,Fthis, this is completely unfair. It is
OL,9,Fnot the country that I think we aspire
OL,10,Fto be. We should stand by our
OL,11,Fpromises."
OL,13,FMr Maynard also expressed concerns
OL,14,Fthat the move could worsen staff
OL,15,Fshortages in critical sectors like the
OL,16,FNHS and social care if workers no
OL,17,Flonger feel welcome or secure.
