OL,6,FThe consultation on the Earned
OL,7,FSettlement proposals, which would
OL,8,Frequire migrants to be in work and
OL,9,Fcontributing for a full decade before
OL,10,Fsettling, closed yesterday.
OL,12,FFor Petra and her family, the outcome
OL,13,Fof that consultation will determine
OL,14,Fwhether their wait to truly call the
OL,15,FUK "home" has just been doubled
